WEBVTT

00:00:01.024 --> 00:00:08.240
THIS IS TAPE EIGHT OF AN INTERVIEW WITH LEE SHULDMAN, JUNE EIGHTH, NINETEEN NINETY-EIGHT, IN BROOKLYN, NEW YORK.

00:00:10.120 --> 00:00:11.143
iz,

00:00:11.773 --> 00:00:14.180
ikh vil bay aykh fregn,

00:00:15.098 --> 00:00:17.820
vos hot ir gehaltn vegn dem plan

00:00:17.820 --> 00:00:20.289
tsu forn tsurik in ayer heym-shtot?

00:00:20.869 --> 00:00:23.833
in mayn heym-shtot hob ikh nit gevelt forn,

00:00:24.430 --> 00:00:27.650
vayl ikh veys az keyner iz lebn nit geblibn,

00:00:27.650 --> 00:00:29.570
un der veytik volt geven

00:00:29.712 --> 00:00:35.781
UNK veytik, az s'iz geve- ⟨ah,⟩ dortn bin ikh geborn un dortn hob ikh farlorn. hob ikh nit gevelt forn.

00:00:36.175 --> 00:00:45.028
un, m'iz geven, ale meydlekh tsuzamen, un me hot geven tsufridn nokh di bafrayung.

00:00:45.642 --> 00:00:49.646
un nakher bin ikh avekgeforn nokh

00:00:49.646 --> 00:00:50.900
Zaltsheym,

00:00:51.666 --> 00:00:57.329
⟨ts-⟩ tsu mayne a khaverte, vos zi iz a, vos mir zaynen geven di zibn meydlekh nokh di bafrayung.

00:00:57.657 --> 00:01:01.729
un zi iz, hot khasene gehat dortn, un ikh bin gekumen ir VISITn,

00:01:01.729 --> 00:01:03.776
un ikh hob zikh bakent mit mayn man.

00:01:04.137 --> 00:01:06.628
er hot mir gezen un m'hot zikh azoy bakent,

00:01:06.651 --> 00:01:07.860
un ikh bin ⟨ts-⟩...

00:01:06.651 --> 00:01:08.906
vi azoy hot ir zikh bakent mit im?

00:01:09.756 --> 00:01:10.851
 vi azoy?

00:01:10.549 --> 00:01:13.276
emetser, hot, geredt a shidekh?

00:01:11.493 --> 00:01:13.161
 i- in Bergen-⟨B-⟩...

00:01:13.161 --> 00:01:13.794
NO.

00:01:13.794 --> 00:01:15.673
 in Bergen-Belzen

00:01:15.730 --> 00:01:20.364
hob ikh bakent a bokher, a Lodzher. m'iz gegangen tantsn, hob ikh bakent im.

00:01:20.607 --> 00:01:22.018
nakher...

00:01:22.041 --> 00:01:23.149
ober

00:01:23.290 --> 00:01:25.987
ikh hob nokh nit gevust vos a libe iz, rikhtik.

00:01:25.987 --> 00:01:27.789
nakher iz er a-...

00:01:26.783 --> 00:01:29.460
vi alt zayt ir geven in der tsayt?

00:01:29.196 --> 00:01:32.902
n- akhtsn-nayntset⟨n⟩ yor, ober n- di milkhome

00:01:33.145 --> 00:01:40.074
un di dos iz, di gedanken zaynen nokh nit geve-, ye. un m'iz geven zeyer naiv a mol.

00:01:40.384 --> 00:01:46.999
amolike mentshn zaynen, meydlekh hot nit gevust vos, haynt veys men, vayle m'hot,...

00:01:47.607 --> 00:01:53.608
iz, nor kh'hob zikh bakent. m'iz gegangen tantsn. efsher hob ikh gehat a gefil tsu im, I DON'T KNOW.

00:01:53.732 --> 00:01:56.054
nakher iz er avekgeforn nokh

00:01:56.297 --> 00:01:57.388
Zaltsheym.

00:01:57.681 --> 00:01:58.333
ye.

00:01:58.660 --> 00:02:13.318
er't mir gerufn, ikh zol forn mit im, ober kh'hob nit gevelt; ⟨do⟩kh er iz nokh nit geven mayn khosn, nit mayn man, hob ikh nit gevelt. un ikh bin do geven tsufridn mit mayn khaverte un gehat, di mame ire iz geven. hot men gegesn tsuzamen un getrunken. iz geven a heym, a shtikl heym.

00:02:14.050 --> 00:02:22.228
un mayn khaverte iz avekgeforn un zi hot khasene gehat in Zaltsheym, un er iz dortn geven. zog ikh, "ikh vel forn tsu ir, vel ikh im oykhet zen."

00:02:22.673 --> 00:02:24.516
 ikh bin gekumen tsu im,

00:02:24.516 --> 00:02:29.332
hot er gezogt az er hot getrofn a meydl vos er iz geven fun Lodzh mit ir,

00:02:29.862 --> 00:02:31.054
fun geto.

00:02:31.819 --> 00:02:35.728
nu, az er hot getrofn yene meydl, bin ikh dokh shoyn ni- nit vikhtik.

00:02:36.537 --> 00:02:40.116
bin ikh avek tsu mayn khaverte, un,...

00:02:40.459 --> 00:02:45.718
un ven, ikh bin geven bay im, iz mayn man aroyf dortn oykhet,

00:02:46.641 --> 00:02:49.312
un er, vayl zey zaynen geven khaveyrim,

00:02:49.403 --> 00:02:51.424
un er't mir gezen, ober

00:02:51.424 --> 00:02:53.154
NOTHING, s'iz a meydl.

00:02:53.154 --> 00:02:57.935
un azoy vi er hot gehert az yener hot gefunen zayn meydl fun Lodzh,

00:02:58.583 --> 00:03:00.343
bin ikh dokh shoyn nit...

00:03:00.709 --> 00:03:03.271
bin ikh gegangen mit mayn khaverte

00:03:03.271 --> 00:03:04.634
oyfn gas

00:03:05.282 --> 00:03:07.655
un er iz ongeforn mit a rover,

00:03:08.134 --> 00:03:10.642
un, "halo," zogt er, "halo."

00:03:10.716 --> 00:03:19.856
un, er hot azoy gekukt azoy. hot mayn khaverte gezogt, "kum aroyf, kum aroyf!", m'iz dokh ale geven azoy, nokh di bafrayung, azoy vi eygene mishpokhe.

00:03:19.862 --> 00:03:21.057
un er iz aroyf.

00:03:21.057 --> 00:03:23.602
un azoy hot zikh farplontert a libe.

00:03:25.605 --> 00:03:31.085
yener nakher iz mit di meydl nit gegangen, vayl yen- di meydl hot shoyn gehat an ander BOY,

00:03:31.085 --> 00:03:32.582
nor zi hot im nit gezogt f⟨UNK⟩.

00:03:32.582 --> 00:03:34.709
un er iz gekumen tsu mir, hob ikh gezogt,

00:03:34.709 --> 00:03:40.933
"az du host gekent geyn tsu yene meydl, az ikh bin bay dir nit geven interesant; i- bistu mir oykh nit interesant."

00:03:41.074 --> 00:03:42.443
un mayn man...

00:03:42.443 --> 00:03:50.535
ober ikh bin nokh nit geven azoy zikher. zog ikh, "ikh for ersht avek tsurik nokh Bergen-Belzen," vayle ikh hob dokh dortn mayn khaverte un ir mame, dos.

00:03:50.625 --> 00:03:55.833
ober, un er hot,... un ikh bin gekumen tsurik un s'iz gevorn a shidekh.

00:03:56.093 --> 00:03:57.403
s'iz gevorn a shid-...

00:03:56.110 --> 00:03:58.047
vi hot er gehey- vi heyst er,

00:03:57.983 --> 00:04:01.487
 Yosef. Yosef Shuldman, ye.

00:03:58.047 --> 00:03:59.158
ayer man?

00:04:01.510 --> 00:04:06.516
un s'iz gevorn a shidekh. ikh hob dortn di PICTURE; kh'vel vayzn di khasene PICTURE fun im mit mir.

00:04:06.943 --> 00:04:10.160
un, m'iz geven in Zaltsheym.

00:04:10.048 --> 00:04:15.813
 iz, fun, funem ershtn, ah, bagegenish bizn, biz der khasene iz geven vi lang?

00:04:16.022 --> 00:04:18.446
nit lang. a fir monat.

00:04:18.587 --> 00:04:19.554
nit lang.

00:04:19.554 --> 00:04:26.344
 yeder eyner hot gezukht mishpokhe. yeder eyner hot gezukht zikh tsutsut-, me zol, makhn a FA- ye.

00:04:26.468 --> 00:04:31.890
⟨iz,⟩ i- ikh bin geven dan, nay- in, dos iz geven in zeks un fertsik,

00:04:31.890 --> 00:04:34.140
 ⟨i-⟩ bin ikh tsvantsik yor geven.

00:04:33.741 --> 00:04:38.021
ver hot ge- ver iz gekumen tsu der khasene? vos far a khasene iz geven?

00:04:36.458 --> 00:04:38.105
der gantser lager.

00:04:38.196 --> 00:04:40.147
der gantser lager. ikh...

00:04:39.141 --> 00:04:42.392
vos far a lager? ⟨d-⟩ di, dos iz geven in Zaltsheym?

00:04:40.238 --> 00:04:50.272
 in Zaltsheym. dos iz shoyn geven fray, ye. in Zaltsheym, ye. in Zaltsheym zaynen di mentshn, hobn di daytshn, hobn gehat daytshishe hayzkes; yeder hot gehat a ROOMke dortn.

00:04:50.413 --> 00:04:52.659
⟨, iz,⟩

00:04:52.659 --> 00:04:54.018
 der,...

00:04:56.269 --> 00:05:03.201
me hot, es iz nit geven in a hiltserner lager, nor in di hayzer fun di daytshn, hot men gegebn far di mentshn.

00:05:03.201 --> 00:05:06.585
s'iz geven efsher a por hundert mentshn dortn in lager, ye.

00:05:06.585 --> 00:05:14.657
un s'iz geven a lager vu s'iz geven a kikh vu me fleg geyn esn dortn un, oder me fleg gebn milkh un broyt, der vos hot nit gevelt esn.

00:05:14.747 --> 00:05:18.757
un s'iz geven a politsey gemakht, azoy vi a,

00:05:18.895 --> 00:05:22.757
⟨a⟩, a sh- shtetl, vi me zogt dos.

00:05:21.564 --> 00:05:25.912
un vi ⟨azoy,⟩ vi ken men bashraybn, di khasene?

00:05:25.378 --> 00:05:27.459
di khasene iz azoy geven:

00:05:27.459 --> 00:05:30.463
koydem hot men ayngeladn ale bakante.

00:05:30.463 --> 00:05:35.345
er, un er, zayne bakante, mayne bakante, ale zaynen gegangen oyf ale khasenes.

00:05:35.487 --> 00:05:38.822
vos iz geven di khasene? s'iz geven dortn a teater,

00:05:39.030 --> 00:05:40.424
a groyser zal,

00:05:40.549 --> 00:05:41.910
hot men gemakht

00:05:42.118 --> 00:05:46.870
m- hot men gekrogn fun lager, az m'iz gegangen khasene, hot der lager gegebn

00:05:46.978 --> 00:05:52.046
produktn, vayl s'iz dokh geven, nokh di krig iz nit geven azoy fil pro- es iz geven oyf di kartn bay di daytshn.

00:05:52.046 --> 00:05:53.210
UNK nit geven.

00:05:53.210 --> 00:05:56.813
nor der lager, az bist gegangen khasene, bist gegangen tsum rov,

00:05:56.813 --> 00:05:59.240
un bist gegangen in mikve, in lager iz geven,

00:05:59.331 --> 00:06:02.767
un me hot gemakht di khasene, opgeredt v-...

00:06:01.778 --> 00:06:03.966
ver iz gegangen mit aykh in mikve?

00:06:03.651 --> 00:06:09.503
iz dortn geven an alt-, a froy a eltere, hot zi mikve... iz men gegangen, un a khaverte.

00:06:08.170 --> 00:06:09.170
UNK

00:06:09.503 --> 00:06:10.934
gedarft geyn in mikve.

00:06:11.245 --> 00:06:14.279
un me hot gemakht di khasene,

00:06:14.279 --> 00:06:22.275
hot men gekrogn, eyer, broyt. hot men gemakht SAND-... s'iz nit geven keyn gekokhte un azoyne khasenes vi haynt,

00:06:22.315 --> 00:06:29.222
ober s'iz geven a MUSIC un s'iz geven, t-, m'hot getantst un me hot, gehat SANDWICHES,

00:06:29.222 --> 00:06:30.782
un m'iz geven tsufridn.

00:06:30.782 --> 00:06:37.726
un a kleyd hob ikh geborgt bay a daytshke, vayle, far a broyt. kh'hob ir gegebn a broyt, hot zi mir gegebn a kleyd. s'iz geven nokh,

00:06:37.726 --> 00:06:39.825
 dan nokh alts oyf kartn.

00:06:39.915 --> 00:06:49.207
un a por shikh hob ikh gehat, vayse, flakhe shikh mit shvartse bendelekh; me lakht a mol, zogt men "di vayse shikh mit shvartse bendelekh," vayl s'iz nit geven vu tsu koyfn.

00:06:49.348 --> 00:06:52.666
un dos iz geven di khasene. hobn mir gemakht di khasene,

00:06:52.943 --> 00:06:54.574
un s'iz geven freylekh.

00:06:54.647 --> 00:06:58.669
ye. oyf keyn HONEYMOON iz men nit geforn,.

00:06:58.669 --> 00:07:01.442
un m'iz geven in Zaltsheym a por yor.

00:07:01.920 --> 00:07:04.192
 nakher hob ikh gehat a meydele,

00:07:04.266 --> 00:07:08.076
ober di meydele iz mir geshtorbn. kh'hob geborn a kind, ye,

00:07:08.076 --> 00:07:09.626
in zibn un fertsik,

00:07:09.666 --> 00:07:14.657
un zi iz geshtorbn. nakher hob ikh geborn, oyf lange yor, mayn zun,

00:07:14.657 --> 00:07:16.545
in akht un fertsik, ye.

00:07:16.770 --> 00:07:20.712
un s'iz gekumen a bafel az me likvidirt dem lager,

00:07:21.006 --> 00:07:22.029
Zaltsheym.

00:07:22.204 --> 00:07:24.071
iz,

00:07:24.870 --> 00:07:29.676
may-, mir zaynen shoyn geven gerufn tsum konsul tsu geyn forn nokh Amerike,

00:07:29.676 --> 00:07:34.246
ober azoy vi m'hot likvidirt dem lager, hot mayn man gezogt, m'vet forn nokh Yisroel.

00:07:34.320 --> 00:07:37.537
iz men gekumen in Yisroel. in Yisroel iz geven...

00:07:37.105 --> 00:07:39.827
vi azoy iz g- geven tsum kumen in Yisroel?

00:07:39.827 --> 00:07:42.008
s'⟨UNK⟩ geven nokh nisht keyn shtot,

00:07:40.834 --> 00:07:41.734
a- azoy:

00:07:41.960 --> 00:07:44.858
es iz nokh, ye. in akht un fertsik iz shoyn geven.

00:07:42.008 --> 00:07:43.376
nokh nisht keyn shtat?

00:07:44.007 --> 00:07:47.612
oh, ⟨s'iz⟩ geven nokh, nokh dem, nokh dem vi es iz gevorn a shtat?

00:07:44.858 --> 00:07:48.990
ikh bin ge- ye, in akht un fertsik. mayn zun hob ikh geborn, ye, in akht un fer-...

00:07:48.990 --> 00:07:53.048
er, mayn ma-, HENRY THERE, iz, er iz geven far di,

00:07:53.048 --> 00:07:54.294
far di, ye.

00:07:54.570 --> 00:07:55.242
ye.

00:07:55.242 --> 00:07:57.129
in akht un fertsik

00:07:57.304 --> 00:08:00.487
iz, bin ikh gekumen in Yisroel.

00:08:00.713 --> 00:08:09.212
iz, s'iz geven di TSENA, un s'iz geven, s'iz geven zeyer shver. kh'hob take gebrakht a bisl zakhn fun Daytshland,

00:08:09.336 --> 00:08:15.152
ober keyn arbet hot er nit gehat, keyn shprakh hot er nit gehat; m'hot dokh nit gekent keyn HEBREW.

00:08:15.512 --> 00:08:19.744
un ⟨s'- m'hot z-⟩ a yor gegesn vos m'hot gehat f-

00:08:19.744 --> 00:08:21.530
eygene gebrakht fun Daytshland.

00:08:21.908 --> 00:08:25.682
un s'iz geven zeyer shver, zeyer shver. far vos?

00:08:25.772 --> 00:08:34.794
vayle s'iz nit geven genug esn oykhet. nokh aza krig, ⟨hos-,⟩ iz geven vayter. s'iz dokh nokh, geven a naye medine.

00:08:35.222 --> 00:08:39.890
un mayn man, iz gegangen pomerantsn raysn,

00:08:40.335 --> 00:08:42.404
un me hot getsolt zeyer veynik.

00:08:42.529 --> 00:08:44.463
un nakher

00:08:44.706 --> 00:08:47.824
hot, iz er gegangen makhn tsigl.

00:08:47.824 --> 00:08:51.618
hobn zey etlekhe mener geefnt azoy vi a fabrikl, tsigl,

00:08:51.709 --> 00:08:54.546
un eyder m'hot nokh gemakht a, a,

00:08:54.546 --> 00:08:58.103
gelt, hot men im tsugenumen in militer far tsvey yor.

00:08:58.560 --> 00:09:02.252
gegangen in militer. iz er avek in militer, bin ikh geblibn mit a kind,

00:09:02.252 --> 00:09:03.751
iz er geven efsher

00:09:04.315 --> 00:09:05.794
a por monatn.

00:09:06.171 --> 00:09:06.944
ye.

00:09:06.944 --> 00:09:10.094
e- e- er iz geven, a, keyn yo- a,

00:09:10.094 --> 00:09:14.484
a, a yor efsher iz er geven, ye. ikh bin gekumen in akht un fertsik, UNK in nayn...

00:09:14.963 --> 00:09:15.820
iz,

00:09:15.820 --> 00:09:17.539
iz oykhet geven shver.

00:09:16.887 --> 00:09:17.589
⟨ir⟩,

00:09:17.950 --> 00:09:20.205
er iz nisht geven in der milkhome, yo?

00:09:19.603 --> 00:09:22.401
NO. dan iz shoyn geven nokh di milkhome, ye.

00:09:20.650 --> 00:09:22.078
⟨es iz shoyn⟩ geven sholem?

00:09:22.401 --> 00:09:25.220
ye. ober tsvey yor host gedarft az me... un,

00:09:24.565 --> 00:09:25.284
⟨⟩.

00:09:25.220 --> 00:09:30.279
un m'iz geven oyfn Negev als militer; a mol, iz oykh geven shiseray tsevishn, ye.

00:09:30.285 --> 00:09:31.876
un nakher, ye.

00:09:31.876 --> 00:09:39.628
iz er geven in militer. nu, militer hot gegebn zeyer veynik gelt, un s'iz geven knap oykh tsum esn. s'iz nit geven laykht; s'iz geven shv-...

00:09:33.105 --> 00:09:34.599
iz, vi,...

00:09:38.571 --> 00:09:41.771
vu, vu hot ir gelebt? m'hot aykh gegebn a dire?

00:09:40.107 --> 00:09:44.002
in BET DAGON, an arabishe, an arabishe voynung.

00:09:44.002 --> 00:09:45.174
un s'iz geven

00:09:45.174 --> 00:09:51.047
di araber vos flegn kumen bay nakht un shekhtn mentshn. s'iz geven, zey hobn dokh, ye.

00:09:51.047 --> 00:09:56.658
un di moyre iz oykh geven. un mit a kind, un er iz geven in militer, un arabishe...

00:09:56.658 --> 00:09:58.523
keyn TOILET iz nit geven in shtub,

00:09:58.523 --> 00:10:02.576
keyn vaser iz nit geven in shtub. s'iz geven, nakher, shpeter hobn zey shoyn gemakht...

00:10:02.576 --> 00:10:05.627
vaser iz in droysn, un a TOILET oykh in droysn.

00:10:05.627 --> 00:10:08.754
s'iz nit geven laykht, der lebn; s'iz geven a shverer lebn.

00:10:08.878 --> 00:10:10.256
un s'iz,

00:10:10.284 --> 00:10:13.243
⟨, un⟩ nakher, i- iz,

00:10:13.401 --> 00:10:15.350
in, ⟨t-⟩

00:10:15.350 --> 00:10:17.563
in tsvey un fuftsikstn

00:10:17.738 --> 00:10:20.364
hob ikh gehat mayn tokhter in Yisroel,

00:10:20.539 --> 00:10:22.291
un er hot zikh bafrayt.

00:10:22.291 --> 00:10:25.370
er iz shoyn ge-, opgedint tsvey yor in militer,

00:10:25.370 --> 00:10:26.828
in tsvey un fuftsik.

00:10:26.935 --> 00:10:36.261
iz er bafrayt gevo-, d- tsvey un fuftsik yanuar., iz er geven nayn un fertsik un, fuftsik un eyn un fuftsik. un tsvey un fuftsik iz er bafrayt gevorn.

00:10:37.650 --> 00:10:38.741
nakher

00:10:38.950 --> 00:10:43.112
iz er arayn bald fun, militer, in POLICE.

00:10:43.219 --> 00:10:44.279
far vos?

00:10:44.279 --> 00:10:46.790
s'iz, er hot gekrogn di,

00:10:46.898 --> 00:10:55.425
 fun militer un POLICE hot er gekrogn azoy, in POLICE a hekhere b- ge- g- batsolt, vayl er hot gehat fun militer

00:10:55.425 --> 00:10:56.657
di,

00:10:56.657 --> 00:10:58.198
 vi UNK zogn?

00:10:58.204 --> 00:11:03.803
azoy vi me arbet oyf a plats kri-, hot men, farzikherung. ⟨m'hot,⟩ iz er...

00:11:01.540 --> 00:11:04.104
aza vi, SENIORITY?

00:11:03.803 --> 00:11:07.614
SENIORITY. iz er ariber tsu POLICE, hot er dos gekrogn.

00:11:07.654 --> 00:11:13.571
un, un er hot z-, er hot shoyn gehat, di meydl iz geborn, un der yingl iz shoyn geven dray a halb yor,

00:11:13.577 --> 00:11:23.065
un zikh, me darf dokh esn. fun mi- fun militer iz men aroys oykh on a peni; nit gekrogn gornit. in militer hot men nor gegebn di,

00:11:23.065 --> 00:11:28.922
far di dire, un di gelt vos m'hot gegebn, tsvantsik funt a monat, iz nit geven genug tsum esn afile.

00:11:28.922 --> 00:11:30.665
un s'iz gevorn di TSENA.

00:11:31.077 --> 00:11:32.691
un,...

00:11:32.477 --> 00:11:33.871
vos iz di TSENA?

00:11:33.692 --> 00:11:43.493
TSENA iz geven oyf kartn, alts oyf kartn. dos hot geheysn di TSENA. s'iz geven ⟨badorfs-⟩, tsaytn. s'iz geven, ⟨hot⟩ gekrogn tsen deko fleysh oyf a kart,

00:11:43.493 --> 00:11:50.224
un gedarft zikh oyfheybn in, far tog, in di LINE shteyn, azoy vi in a milkhome-tsayt. s'iz geven shvere yorn.

00:11:50.584 --> 00:11:53.254
ober, s'hot zikh alts ibergedreyt.

00:11:53.254 --> 00:11:57.750
nakher iz bafrayt gevorn, er iz gegangen in POLICE. nakher hot men gekrogn a SHIKUN.

00:11:58.397 --> 00:12:00.081
a SHIKUN, dos ⟨i-⟩

00:11:59.511 --> 00:12:00.399
vos iz dos?

00:12:00.081 --> 00:12:02.584
dos heyst, naye hayzkes geboyt.

00:12:02.633 --> 00:12:06.300
hot men oykh nit gegebn alemen; me hot gedarft... iz azoy vi

00:12:06.300 --> 00:12:08.519
ikh hob gehat, er hot gehat a kuzin,

00:12:08.519 --> 00:12:11.486
iz er oykh aroys fun militer; iz der kuzin...

00:12:11.526 --> 00:12:16.937
un ikh hob shoyn tsvey kinder, un er fun milite- hob ikh gekrogn, a SHIKUN.

00:12:16.977 --> 00:12:21.374
hot men gedarft batsoln toyznt, funt.. s'iz dan geven...

00:12:21.374 --> 00:12:22.894
hob ikh nit gehat keyn peni.

00:12:23.659 --> 00:12:28.204
ober dos iz geven aza gelegnheyt, a SHIKUN tsu krign, az mentshn...

00:12:28.204 --> 00:12:34.892
hob ikh ongeborgt vi di velt iz groys: ⟨,⟩ bay a kuzinke iz geven eyne, un bay dem un bay fremde un bay dos...

00:12:35.100 --> 00:12:40.885
un ikh hob opgetsolt, ober ikh hob nit dergesn. ikh hob opgetsolt di ge- di toyznt funt dan.

00:12:40.885 --> 00:12:42.674
dos iz geven in,

00:12:42.674 --> 00:12:46.873
in tsvey un fuftsik., dan iz dos geven gelt, toyznt funt.

00:12:47.014 --> 00:12:57.605
un e- er hot gemakht efsher zi- tsvey un zibetsik a monat, tsvey un zibetsik funt. iz dos geven a sakh gelt. s'iz nit keyn sakh, ober s'iz a sakh geven far mir, un ikh hob nit gehat.

00:12:57.612 --> 00:12:59.972
kh'hob zikh gut, gut ongematert.

00:12:59.972 --> 00:13:01.725
gut, gut, gut ongematert.

00:13:01.725 --> 00:13:02.755
shpeter

00:13:02.755 --> 00:13:04.468
iz avek a bisl yorn,

00:13:04.468 --> 00:13:06.332
hot zikh shoyn, farbesert.

00:13:07.429 --> 00:13:09.058
er hot fardint mer,

00:13:09.058 --> 00:13:13.538
un, ikh hob gevelt geyn arbetn. s'iz nit geven vu tsu arbetn. s'iz nit geven.

00:13:13.538 --> 00:13:15.779
kh'hob gezukht a JOB; s'iz nit geven.

00:13:15.921 --> 00:13:19.799
un, ikh hob gekrogn nakher fun Daytshland,

00:13:19.799 --> 00:13:21.247
hob ikh gekrogn gelt,

00:13:22.283 --> 00:13:23.660
 fun....

00:13:22.620 --> 00:13:23.643
vi azoy?

00:13:23.953 --> 00:13:29.077
me k-, s'iz geven ⟨o-⟩, m'hot farshribn az, m'hot zikh registrirt.

00:13:29.151 --> 00:13:33.532
un nakher iz avek a bisl yor, hobn zey getsolt, ye.

00:13:33.775 --> 00:13:37.464
hob ikh shoyn a bisl zikh, farbesert.

00:13:37.483 --> 00:13:38.261
ye.

00:13:37.611 --> 00:13:41.328
dos, bay vifl, bay dem vifltn hot ir genumen

00:13:41.672 --> 00:13:43.455
hobn gelt fun Daytshland?

00:13:44.305 --> 00:13:51.622
dos iz geven efsher in finf un fuftsik, in zekhs-, in etlekhe un fuftsikstn yor; fun Daytshland hob ikh gekrogn gelt, ye.

00:13:47.140 --> 00:13:47.713
⟨⟩.

00:13:51.966 --> 00:13:53.659
hob ikh shoyn, ye.

00:13:53.659 --> 00:13:58.936
un er hot shoyn fardint beser un, s'iz shoyn geven, ye.

00:13:58.665 --> 00:13:59.808
UNK

00:13:58.936 --> 00:14:01.005
s'iz shoyn geven, ikh hob...

00:13:59.998 --> 00:14:01.949
di lage iz gevorn a bisl beser?

00:14:01.483 --> 00:14:03.454
ye, s'iz gevorn beser, ye.

00:14:03.454 --> 00:14:08.264
un, ven ikh bin zikh gegang- un, ven s'iz geven mir azoy shlekht, rikhtik,

00:14:08.264 --> 00:14:12.938
kh'hob nit gehat, iz er avek zikh registrirn nokh Amerike tsu forn,

00:14:12.938 --> 00:14:16.260
vayle s'iz mir nit geven gut, ye.

00:14:16.300 --> 00:14:18.288
ober ven ikh bin gegangen

00:14:18.288 --> 00:14:22.599
iz di kvote vos iz geven fun Daytshland, iz shoyn geven farlorn,

00:14:22.599 --> 00:14:28.798
vayl dos i- ikh bin geven in Yisroel. ven ikh volt bald gegangen in konsul, volt men mir gemakht di kvote, ober

00:14:28.973 --> 00:14:31.363
kh'hob gelozn avekgeyn di kvote.

00:14:31.375 --> 00:14:33.003
s'- s'iz finf yor.

00:14:31.555 --> 00:14:32.949
vos heyst...?

00:14:33.003 --> 00:14:39.429
⟨a- a-,⟩ az ikh hob zikh farshribn in Yisroel oyf a kvote tsu forn nokh Amerike, hot finf yor genumen

00:14:39.722 --> 00:14:44.593
bizkl s'iz gekumen ⟨KVOTOT⟩, vey- azoy, grupn v⟨u⟩ me shikt, ye.

00:14:44.717 --> 00:14:48.373
nu, durkh di finf yor hobn mir shoyn gevorn beser, hob ikh nit gevelt forn.

00:14:48.852 --> 00:14:55.106
hob, hob ikh eyn mol nit gegangen tsum konsul ⟨az⟩ m'hot mir gerufn, un nokh a mol. dem dritn mol, me zogt, tomer kum ikh nit,

00:14:55.500 --> 00:14:58.177
farmakhn zey, vel ikh nit kenen forn.

00:14:58.369 --> 00:15:04.725
bin ikh... zogt mayn man, "du for mit di meydl," mit di klenere, un er vet blaybn mitn zun,

00:15:04.900 --> 00:15:07.048
un ikh'l forn zen

00:15:07.048 --> 00:15:11.559
vos do iz. ikh bin gekumen do, bin ikh gekumen take tsu mayn khaverte in Minesote,

00:15:11.616 --> 00:15:19.451
un ikh hob genumen bald arbetn, un ikh hob gezen az, s'iz be- laykhter do vi, vi, vi, dan iz shoyn mir geven laykhter.

00:15:19.451 --> 00:15:22.764
ober STILL, az bald der onheyb iz geven laykhter...

00:15:23.175 --> 00:15:26.918
iz er nakher gekumen in a finf monatn shpeter,

00:15:26.918 --> 00:15:29.970
iz er gekumen, ye. ikh bin do gekumen in SIXTY,

00:15:29.976 --> 00:15:32.790
 in JULY, in JUNE.

00:15:32.790 --> 00:15:36.567
ye. ven di SCHOOL hot zikh geendikt bin ikh geforn mit mayn tokhter, ye.

00:15:36.625 --> 00:15:39.195
un er iz gekumen,

00:15:39.195 --> 00:15:42.424
nakher, ye, bayn ende yor.

00:15:41.907 --> 00:15:43.841
iz, ir hot bashlosn tsu blaybn?

00:15:43.543 --> 00:15:47.739
un nakher bashlosn, un azoy hot men zikh, got tsu danken, ayngeordnt.

00:15:48.066 --> 00:15:49.325
ye, ikh hob in...

00:15:48.606 --> 00:15:49.308
in,

00:15:49.618 --> 00:15:50.495
⟨ave-⟩

00:15:49.635 --> 00:15:57.375
in Yisroel hot ir, zayt ir gut oysgekumen mit di, di sabres? ho- ir hot gehat tsu ton mit, ah, dort?

00:15:55.963 --> 00:16:03.199
NO, mir zaynen MOST geven mit undzere mentshn. MOST zaynen ge- di sabres zaynen fayne mentshn; me ken nit, zogn ⟨az zey zaynen nit⟩, ye.

00:16:03.199 --> 00:16:10.469
MOST iz men geven alts eyne, in dorf dortn, in BET DAGON, iz alts geven ge- gekumene.

00:16:10.543 --> 00:16:13.695
un in di SHIKUNIM iz oykhet di mentshn vos dos.

00:16:13.695 --> 00:16:21.489
az ikh bin shoyn aroys in, RAMAT GAN... nakher bin ikh aroys, ven ikh hob, farkoyft dem SHIKUN, ikh bin aroys tsu RAMAT GAN. ikh hob gehat a BAYIT MESHUTAF...

00:16:21.546 --> 00:16:23.028
hob ikh gehat sabres.

00:16:23.028 --> 00:16:31.788
ober zey zaynen geven fayn. may⟨ne a⟩ shokhnte iz geven a sabre, un oybn ⟨s- es⟩ zaynen geven fayne... ikh hob gelebt mit zey gut, ye. kh'hob gehat mit zey gute batsiungen, ye.

00:16:31.249 --> 00:16:34.162
iz, sakh-hakl, vos, mit vos far a,

00:16:34.302 --> 00:16:38.026
, a bild zayt ir geblibn fun Yisroel?

00:16:38.455 --> 00:16:41.469
mit, ⟨un⟩ vos far a FEELING zayt ir geblibn?

00:16:40.648 --> 00:16:44.644
ikh hob lib Yisroel. ikh hob nit, bin nit geven in kaas oyf Yisroel.

00:16:44.644 --> 00:16:51.631
kh'hob nit gevelt avekforn afile, ober s'iz mir geven azoy, tsaytn azoy shlekht, rikhtik, fun onheyb, ⟨⟩, zeyer shl- ye.

00:16:51.631 --> 00:16:52.387
ober

00:16:52.663 --> 00:16:56.626
s'iz ge-, dos iz geven azoy. vos hob ikh gekent ton?

00:16:56.626 --> 00:16:57.858
ye. ye.

00:16:58.688 --> 00:17:00.639
un dan vos hot pasirt,

00:17:00.797 --> 00:17:04.773
mit ayer lebn, in, in Amerike? vos hot ir geton?

00:17:02.767 --> 00:17:04.611
in, in Amerike?

00:17:04.611 --> 00:17:07.215
hot mayn man gearbet un ikh hob gearbet,

00:17:07.215 --> 00:17:10.045
un mir hobn zikh bald,

00:17:10.045 --> 00:17:12.266
s'hot undz nit gefelt keyn groshn.

00:17:11.226 --> 00:17:13.262
vos hot ir geton far arbet?

00:17:13.116 --> 00:17:19.221
 ikh bin geven, ikh bin gegangen in, in a HOME hob ikh gearbet. kh'hob dokh keyn fakh nit gehat.

00:17:19.221 --> 00:17:22.208
in a HOME. un bay nakht bin ikh gegangen in SCHOOL.

00:17:22.208 --> 00:17:24.351
kh'hob gevelt endikn far a NURSE,

00:17:24.351 --> 00:17:30.089
ober vi ikh hob ongehoybn SCHOOL, un mayn man, un tsvey kinder in SCHOOL gegangen,

00:17:30.089 --> 00:17:36.138
un ikh hob gedarft forn mitn TRAIN fun onheyb un alts, un ikh bin gekumen nakher, gelofn in SCHOOL un esn...

00:17:36.138 --> 00:17:39.269
⟨s'iz⟩ geven tsu shver oykhet; s'iz nit geven laykht.

00:17:39.269 --> 00:17:40.497
un nakher

00:17:40.504 --> 00:17:45.864
iz, mayn man gevorn krank; bay FIFTY-TWO hot er gekrogn a harts-atak.

00:17:46.647 --> 00:17:57.053
un tsen yor iz er geven krank. hob ikh shoyn fargesn fun a SCHOOL tsu geyn; ikh hob gevelt g⟨e-⟩ lerenen far a NURSE. bin ikh shoyn geblibn bay dem fakh, vayl ikh hob shoyn gedarft hobn di farzikherung,

00:17:57.193 --> 00:18:02.570
mit, mit di meditsin. hob ikh shoyn gornit geklert un ikh hob shoyn gemuzt azoy onhaltn.

00:18:02.998 --> 00:18:10.569
un, er iz geshtorbn, iz er geven SIXTY-TWO. tsen yor iz er geven krank, un tsen yor bin ikh geven aleyn.

00:18:10.238 --> 00:18:15.109
 ir, ober, ir hot gehat nokh a kind do in Amerike?

00:18:10.812 --> 00:18:11.936
ober ikh hob...

00:18:12.352 --> 00:18:13.352
?

00:18:14.727 --> 00:18:18.940
NO, NO. mayn zun un mayn tokhter. UNK tokhter in Yisroel, un mayn zun.

00:18:16.465 --> 00:18:17.767
dos iz alts.

00:18:19.080 --> 00:18:27.056
ober, un ikh hob vayter gearbet, un ikh bin gegangen, ikh bin gekumen, ikh bin geforn, un ikh hob m- gemakht mayn lebn di best vos kh'hob gekent.

00:18:27.130 --> 00:18:30.080
vi azoy hot zikh antviklt az ir zayt do in Nyu-York,

00:18:30.080 --> 00:18:31.292
avek fun,

00:18:31.450 --> 00:18:32.659
MINNESOTA?

00:18:31.500 --> 00:18:36.539
ikh hob nit geglikhn Minesote. far vos? s'iz a SU-, vu zi hot gevoynt iz a SUBURB.

00:18:38.520 --> 00:18:45.199
zey zaynen shoyn tsugeveynt geven dortn. zey hobn gehat hayzkes, zaynen geven tsugevoynt tsu aza le-... ikh bin gekumen ersht UNK,

00:18:45.199 --> 00:18:49.064
un do hob ikh gehat a por bakante, un ikh glaykh a CITY mer,

00:18:49.064 --> 00:18:55.777
un do iz geven yidish mer; do iz geven, in NEW YORK, BROOKLYN, geven a yidish, a sakh yidn.

00:18:55.902 --> 00:19:01.763
iz, hob ikh liber gehat vi dortn, tsu zayn in a SUBURB, ye.

00:19:01.763 --> 00:19:06.493
un azoy ⟨z-⟩ bin ikh geblibn, bin ikh geven in eyn APARTMENT, in a tsveytn

00:19:06.533 --> 00:19:09.494
nakher, biz kh'hob gekoyft di hoyz, ye.

00:19:09.418 --> 00:19:12.445
un vi lang zayt ir do in der, in dem sheynem hoyz?

00:19:10.617 --> 00:19:12.891
in di hoyz? tsvey un draysik yor.

00:19:12.891 --> 00:19:13.580
ye.

00:19:13.603 --> 00:19:19.683
gekoyft, un dos iz fun mir mit mayn man, fun undzere beyde hent; m'hot gearbet un m'hot avekgeleygt a groshn

00:19:19.683 --> 00:19:21.545
un m'hot gehit a groshn.

00:19:21.568 --> 00:19:28.644
un THANK GOD, m'hot khasene gemakht di kinder, hot men geholfn. un, di eyniklekh geyen in SCHOOL, un m'hot ge- m'hot ge-...

00:19:28.644 --> 00:19:29.733
un THANK GOD,

00:19:29.733 --> 00:19:32.869
alts fun eygene tsen hent; keyner hot mir nit gegebn.

00:19:34.461 --> 00:19:35.614
iz,

00:19:34.840 --> 00:19:35.840
d⟨i⟩...

00:19:35.614 --> 00:19:37.023
hot ir,

00:19:37.023 --> 00:19:41.306
epes vos tsu zogn, vegn dem vos, vi azoy

