iz geblibn di shrek ale mol

00:19:50.965 --> 00:19:56.662
un di moyre. derfar hot men gehaltn a groshn, vayle m'hot gevust az keyner vet dir nit gebn, un az du host nit...

00:19:56.753 --> 00:19:57.455
ye.

00:19:57.478 --> 00:20:01.218
hostu gehaltn zikh, un biz haynt... un aroysvarfn esn

00:20:01.275 --> 00:20:03.176
iz nokh oykhet aza...

00:20:03.368 --> 00:20:05.134
i- ikh ken nit aroysvarfn.

00:20:05.781 --> 00:20:09.639
un ⟨i-⟩ vifl m-, ye. ikh ken nit aroysvarfn.

00:20:09.645 --> 00:20:10.297
ye.

00:20:10.438 --> 00:20:16.147
ober, a mol iz do zakhn vos s'iz shoyn zoyer, me muz aroysvarfn, ober s'iz azoy alts, vos s'iz nokh...

00:20:16.147 --> 00:20:20.332
azoy vi mayn tokhter hot aroysgevorfn a tsibele, s'iz geven a bisele tsefoylt,

00:20:20.332 --> 00:20:25.429
hob ikh aroysgenumen di tsibele. zog ikh, "kenstu dos opshnaydn, un me ken dokh ⟨i- nitsn⟩."

