mir zaynen dokh durkh hunger un kelt un krankeytn un veytikn un... s'iz dokh,

00:20:41.257 --> 00:20:46.393
rikh- un zoln zey zayn, un derfar vil men az zey zol zayn beser un beser.

00:20:46.416 --> 00:20:50.595
git men zey, helft men a mol, un me TRYt di best, ye.

00:20:51.242 --> 00:20:51.776
un...

00:20:51.276 --> 00:20:53.092
iz, ir hot,

