I'M SURPRISED, ⟨ikh ho-⟩... e- er ligt, un ikh hob nit geendikt.

00:21:21.533 --> 00:21:23.602
ye. un ikh ken im nit derendikn.

00:21:23.640 --> 00:21:24.496
ye.

00:21:24.640 --> 00:21:31.331
un i- ale tog hob ikh shoyn aroysgenumen, zog ikh, "ikh..." un ikh ken im nit derendikn. un s'iz shoyn rikhtik nit keyn sakh tsu derendikn; kh'hob geredt,

00:21:31.388 --> 00:21:32.841
..

